Architecture: all
Maintainer: Al Audet <alaudet@linuxnorth.org>
Installed-Size: 40
Depends: python3:any, python3-lgpio
Section: python
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/alaudet/pinsource
Description: HC-SR04 ultrasonic sensor driver for Raspberry Pi
 pinsource provides a Python interface for HC-SR04 ultrasonic distance
 sensors on Raspberry Pi, using lgpio for GPIO access. It supports metric
 and imperial measurements, depth and volume calculations, and is compatible
 with Raspberry Pi 5 and all models supported by lgpio.
